job_description: Our client in the insurance space is looking for a Software Developer who is eager to help them advance their cloud-native services platform. The role will be 100% remote and your development efforts will be applied to back-end API and front-end browser-based application features. Their tech stacks include typescript, nest.js, docker, MongoDB, and vue.js. Their push button CI/CD pipelines make easy work of deployments to their container microservices infrastructure.The team is a fantastic group of professionals who look forward to bringing on an ambitious individual who is always looking for new problems to solve.
